@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wtvjkl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos((v2 + 0.85 * v1 + 0.90)))
    v2 = 0.62
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp((tmp + 0.47 + tmp + 0.77)))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.abs(v1 + 0.49) - (v1 + 0.18 / v2 + 0.69)))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
